DefaultReaderConfiguration.preQueryCheck: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "PUB"."_aud-audit-data" ad WHERE ad."_Audit-date-time" > ?
DefaultReaderConfiguration.queryString: SELECT CAST(TO_CHAR(ad."_Audit-date-time",'yyyy-mm-dd hh:mi:ss') AS TIMESTAMP) AS 'ResultScanDate', ae."_Event-id", ae."_Event-name", ae."_Event-description", ae."_Event-type", ad."_User-id", ad."_Db-guid", ad."_Event-detail", ap."_Audit-policy-name", adv."_Field-name", adv."_Old-string-value", adv."_New-string-value", cs."_Client-name" AS '_CS-Client-name', cs."_User-id" AS '_CS-User-id', CAST(TO_CHAR(cs."_Authentication-date-time",'yyyy-mm-dd hh:mi:ss') AS TIMESTAMP) AS '_CS-Auth-date-time', cs."_Authentication-domain-type" AS '_CS-Authentication-domain-type', cs."_Authentication-domain-name" AS '_CS-Authentication-domain-name', cs."_Authentication-domain-type" AS '_CS-Authentication-domain-type', cs."_Db-guid" AS '_CS-Db-guid' FROM "PUB"."_aud-audit-data" ad LEFT OUTER JOIN "PUB"."_aud-audit-data-value" adv ON adv."_Audit-data-guid" = ad."_Audit-data-guid" LEFT OUTER JOIN "PUB"."_aud-event" ae ON ae."_Event-id" = ad."_Event-id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "PUB"."_aud-event-policy" ep ON ep."_Event-id" = ad."_Event-id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "PUB"."_aud-audit-policy" ap ON ap."_Audit-policy-guid" = ep."_Audit-policy-guid" LEFT OUTER JOIN "PUB"."_client-session" cs ON cs."_Client-session-uuid" = ad."_Client-session-uuid" WHERE ad."_Audit-date-time" > ? ORDER BY ad."_Audit-date-time"

string.toolTipText: Date and time in milliseconds since epoch
